# Git LFS rules for the v1 UI catalog (ADR-010, issue #79).
#
# WebP screenshots committed under docs/legacy/v1-ui-catalog/ are stored via
# Git LFS. Captions, READMEs, and the run manifest stay in regular git.
# Contributors: run `git lfs install` once after cloning. CONTRIBUTING.md
# documents the setup. CI workflows that do not need to view the catalog
# binaries should skip LFS smudging via `LFS_SKIP_SMUDGE=1`.

docs/legacy/v1-ui-catalog/**/*.webp filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
